<l>parivati līcaṉaip pāṭi</l>
<l>virivatu mēva luṟuvīr</l>
<l>pirivakai yiṉṟinaṉ ṉīrtūy</l>
<l>purivatu vumpukai pūvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Singing the lord without suffering,</l>
<l>experience/undertake being attached to spreading</l>
<l>incense [and] flowers and in performing</l>
<l>by sprinkling good water without [any] kind of separation.</l>
      </lg>
